# Agent Tool Usage Rules

## Context7 MCP — Always Validate
Before implementing anything involving an external library (FastAPI, Pydantic, Vue, Docker, etc.):
1. `resolve-library-id` → get library ID
2. `query-docs` → fetch authoritative docs
3. Validate your implementation matches the fetched docs

## Code Navigation — LSP First
```
LSP (pyright/volar/vtsls) → grep/glob → Read+scan
```
- Use LSP symbol search before grep/glob/bash for finding definitions.
- Only fall back to grep for non-code text search or regex patterns.

## NPX — Use Wrapper
```bash
# ✅ Always
/home/mac/.claude/bin/nvm-npx -y <package>

# ❌ Never
npx <package>
node /hardcoded/path
```

## Docker Compose (Dev)
```bash
# Start with live file watch (recommended)
./dev.sh watch

# Follow logs
./dev.sh logs -f backend
```

